Class ThreadNode<IN,OUT>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.robopupu.api.graph.Node<IN,OUT>
      • com.robopupu.api.graph.nodes.ThreadNode<IN,OUT>
  • Type Parameters:
    IN - The type of input value.
    OUT - The type of output value.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    InputNode<IN>, OutputNode<OUT>

    public class ThreadNode<IN,OUT>
extends Node<IN,OUT>
    ThreadNode implements a Node that can be used to transfer execution to a worker Thread or to main Thread.
